# Paths oxfmt must never format, beyond what .gitignore already covers.
#
# Two consumers pass this file via --ignore-path:
#   1. The gen pipeline's `formatDir` passes ONLY this file, so it can still
#      format the git-ignored `temp/` and the generated `output*/` dirs by their
#      explicit paths (none of which are listed here).
#   2. The repo-wide `fmt` script passes `.gitignore` AND this file, so it skips
#      the usual build artifacts plus the tracked paths below.
node_modules/
pnpm-lock.yaml
agents/
docs/
